{"word":"G749 - ἀρχιερεύς - archiereús - ar-khee-er-yuce' - Chief priest","slug":"G749","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀρχιερεύς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>archiereús"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ar-khee-er-yuce'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Chief priest"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C1;&#x03C7;&#x03B9;&#x03B5;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C2; - archiereus</b> - <i>ar-khee-er-yuce'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G746\">G746</a> and <a href=\"#/G2409\">G2409</a>; the <i>high priest</i> (literally of the Jews, typically Christ); by extension a <i>chief priest:</i> - chief (high) priest, chief of the priests."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1494\">G1494</a>, <a href=\"#/G2405\">G2405</a>, <a href=\"#/G2406\">G2406</a>, <a href=\"#/G2407\">G2407</a>, <a href=\"#/G2409\">G2409</a>, <a href=\"#/G2411\">G2411</a>, <a href=\"#/G2412\">G2412</a>, <a href=\"#/G2413\">G2413</a>, <a href=\"#/G2416\">G2416</a>, <a href=\"#/G2417\">G2417</a>, <a href=\"#/G2418\">G2418</a>, <a href=\"#/G2420\">G2420</a>"}]}